sourcesContent: import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card' import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col' import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button' import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'; import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row' import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux' const CardTodo = ( {done, date, description} ) => { const dispatch = useDispatch() return ( {date} {description} ) } export default CardTodo
